snippet: Kyle Busch led from start to finish, usually by plenty, and ended an eight-race NASCAR Nationwide Series winless streak Friday night with his fifth career victory at Richmond International Raceway....

headline.print_headline: Kyle Busch Never Trails in Victory at Richmond
headline.main: Kyle Busch Never Trails in Victory at Richmond

lead_paragraph: Kyle Busch led from start to finish, usually by plenty, and ended an eight-race NASCAR Nationwide Series winless streak Friday night with his fifth career victory at Richmond International Raceway.
